State Regulations

The provisions of this Part shall not apply to proof of
financial security that has been provided to the commissioner under articles 6
and 8 of the Vehicle and Traffic Law by means other than an insurance policy, such as, financial security deposits made under section
314
of
the Vehicle and Traffic Law and self-insurers authorized under section
316
of
